## JSON Schema para Vista General del Kanban

### Estructura Principal

```json
{
  "id": "string",
  "title": "string",
  "description": "string",
  "status": "string",
  "createdBy": "string",
  "createdAt": "date",
  "quarter": "string",
  "score": "number",
  "category": "string",
  "vertical": "string",
  "clientType": "string",
  "country": "string",
  "systemicRisk": "string",
  "economicImpact": "string",
  "economicImpactDescription": "string",
  "experienceImpact": "array",
  "competitiveApproach": "string",
  "executiveSummary": "string",
  "roi": "number"
}
```

### Valores Posibles para Cada Campo

#### Category (Categoría)
```json
{
  "category": "Mandates / Regulatorio / Riesgo" | "Mejora de performance" | "Value Prop" | "Lanzamiento nuevo producto"
}
```

#### Vertical
```json
{
  "vertical": "Processing" | "Core" | "BIN Sponsor" | "Card Management & Logistics" | "Tokenización" | "Fraud Tools" | "Platform experience"
}
```

#### Tipo de Cliente
```json
{
  "clientType": "Todos" | "Top Issuer" | "Tier 1" | "Tier 2" | "Tier 3"
}
```

#### País
```json
{
  "country": "Todos" | "Argentina" | "Brasil" | "Chile" | "Colombia" | "Mexico" | "ROLA"
}
```

#### Riesgo Sistémico
```json
{
  "systemicRisk": "Bloqueante" | "Alto" | "Medio" | "Bajo" | "N/A"
}
```

#### Impacto Económico
```json
{
  "economicImpact": "Aumento significativo en revenue o nueva linea revenue" | "Aumento moderado en revenue existente" | "Impacto menor o dificil de cuantificar"
}
```

#### Impacto en Experiencia (Array)
```json
{
  "experienceImpact": ["Contact Rate", "Aprobación", "Aceptación", "Provisioning Rate", "SLA de envíos", "SLA de incidencias", "BPS (Chargebacks)", "Revisión Manual KYC"]
}
```

#### Enfoque Competitivo
```json
{
  "competitiveApproach": "Disrrustivo / Innovador" | "Mejora incremental" | "Paridad con competencia"
}
```

