### Endpoints Sugeridos para CRUD

#### GET - Obtener iniciativa
```
GET /api/initiatives/:id
```

#### PUT - Actualizar iniciativa
```
PUT /api/initiatives/:id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "Mejora de performance",
  "vertical": "Core",
  "clientType": "Top Issuer",
  "country": "Mexico",
  "systemicRisk": "Medio",
  "economicImpact": "Aumento moderado en revenue existente",
  "economicImpactDescription": "Mejora en eficiencia que generará $500K adicionales",
  "experienceImpact": ["Contact Rate", "Aprobación"],
  "competitiveApproach": "Mejora incremental",
  "executiveSummary": "Nueva descripción del resumen ejecutivo...",
  "roi": 150
}
```

#### PATCH - Actualizar campos específicos
```
PATCH /api/initiatives/:id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roi": 400,
  "systemicRisk": "Bajo"
}
```

